ZH: 我将继承父母的公司。
EN: I will inherit my parents' company.
 
ZH: 这块地将被我继承。
EN: This land will be inherited by me.
 
ZH: 公司的继承人应具备管理技能。
EN: The heir of the company should have management skills.
 
ZH: 继承遗产需要支付一定的遗产税。
EN: Inheriting an estate requires paying certain inheritance taxes.
 
ZH: 他将继承家族的家传技艺。
EN: He will inherit the family's traditional skills.
 
ZH: 继承一个家族的财富是一项重大责任。
EN: Inheriting a family's wealth is a great responsibility.
 
ZH: 我希望能继承母亲的明亮眼睛。
EN: I hope to inherit my mother's bright eyes.
 
ZH: 这些古老的传统将继承下去。
EN: These ancient traditions will be inherited.
 
ZH: 继承不仅仅意味着财富，而且还有责任。
EN: Inheritance doesn't just mean wealth, it also comes with responsibility.
 
ZH: 他是我继承的那位亲戚。
EN: He is the relative I inherited from.
 
ZH: 她继承了父亲的商业帝国。
EN: She inherited her father's business empire.
 
ZH: 继承权应该按照法律规定来行使。
EN: The right of inheritance should be exercised according to the law.
 
ZH: 谁将继承公司的股权？
EN: Who will inherit the shares of the company?
 
ZH: 继承一个王朝的王位是一项重大的责任。
EN: Inheriting the throne of a dynasty is a great responsibility.
 
ZH: 我很自豪能继承祖辈的传统。
EN: I am proud to inherit the traditions of my ancestors.
 
ZH: 遗产应该按照遗嘱进行继承。
EN: Inheritance should be carried out according to the will.
 
ZH: 她继承了家族中的医生传统。
EN: She inherited the medical tradition in her family.
 
ZH: 每个人都有权利继承他们合法的财产。
EN: Everyone has the right to inherit their legitimate property.
 
ZH: 继承家族事业是我的梦想。
EN: Inheriting the family business is my dream.
 
ZH: 继承文化遗产是我们的责任。
EN: Inheriting cultural heritage is our responsibility.
